          "text": "Shadowfield: You cannot re-roll invulnerable saving throws made for the bearer. The first time an invulnerable saving throw made for the bearer is failed, until the end of the battle, the bearer has no invulnerable save. Soul Trap: Add 1 to the Attacks and Strength characteristics of the bearer\u2019s melee weapons. The first time the bearer makes a melee attack that destroys an enemy model, after all the bearer\u2019s attacks have been resolved, until the end of the battle, add an additional 1 to the Attacks and Strength characteristics of the bearer\u2019s melee weapons."
